<XMLDocContent PageName="ExodusSDK.Overview" Title="Overview of Exodus SDK" xmlns="http://www.exodusemulator.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The Exodus SDK is a set of support libraries that allow communication with the Exodus Platform. All communication between plugins and the
      platform itself happens through a set of pure virtual interfaces, which allows plugins to be developed, compiled, and deployed separately from
      the platform itself.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      Note that the Exodus Platform itself is also a separate component, which is isolated from the platform and user interface. The SDK also contains
      the necessary interfaces to communicate with the Exodus Platform and implement an overall user interface to manage it.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
